data.description: A fabulous opportunity for Investors and First-Time Home Buyers!  Discover this charming 2-bedroom, 1-bath home located in the heart of Gooding. With the Little Wood River just across the street and no front neighbors, you can enjoy the peaceful sounds of your surroundings. The beautiful Hideout Park is just a short drive away. Additional features include alley access and the potential for a third bedroom in the basement. Don't wait to schedule a visit – call today!
